Interface MessageListenerInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
MessageQueueManager, QueueManager, TesterQueueManager 
public interface MessageListenerInterface

Author:
Bala Maniymaran Created: 2010-08-12 This specifies the interface of a message listener object. A message listener should register itself with a message receiver so that the message receiver can inform the message listener of new messages using the interface. Note that the message receiver can be anything: it can be a communication server or it can be another message listener.
See Also:
